#####################################
# Lyrics Management API
#####################################

### Lyrics Management - Get Full Collection
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lyrics-management/collections
Accept: application/json

###

### Lyrics Management - Search Songs (Empty Query)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lyrics-management/songs?maxResults=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Lyrics Management - Search Songs (With Query)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lyrics-management/songs?query=love&maxResults=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Lyrics Management - Get Song by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lyrics-management/songs/wu_tang_clan_-_c.r.e.a.m
Accept: application/json

###

### Lyrics Management - Get All Artists
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lyrics-management/artists
Accept: application/json

###

### Lyrics Management - Get All Albums
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lyrics-management/albums
Accept: application/json

###

### Lyrics Management - Get Collection Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lyrics-management/collections/stats
Accept: application/json

###

### Lyrics Management - Regenerate Collection
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/lyrics-management/collections/regenerate

###

#####################################
# Speech Synthesis API
#####################################

### Speech - Test Configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Speech/test-config
Accept: application/json

###

### Speech - Synthesize Speech
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Speech
Content-Type: application/json

"Good morrow, fair world, how dost thou fare?"

###

### Speech - Synthesize Empty Text (Should Return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Speech
Content-Type: application/json

""

###

### Speech - Synthesize Long Text
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Speech
Content-Type: application/json

"Good morrow, kind sir. Prithee, might I inquire as to thy well-being on this fine day? The weather doth appear most favorable for a leisurely promenade through the verdant gardens."

